About
/$
$
Welcome to The Original Crazy Horse Saloon,
Your Favorite Neighborhood Bar
, where good times and great company come together! Nestled in the heart of the community, we pride ourselves on offering a warm and inviting atmosphere with top-notch food and drinks.
At Crazy Horse Saloon, we create a welcoming space for everyone by maintaining a smoke-free environment. Our menu features a range of delicious food options and craft beverages, with daily specials that are sure to delight.
Whether you’re joining us for a casual bite, a celebratory drink, or just to catch up with friends, there’s always something exciting happening here.
​
From lively events like trivia, bingo or karaoke, to our live music nights, we keep our calendar full of activities designed to bring people together. Be sure to check out our events page to stay updated on what’s coming up.
